<br>
&quot;Thank you for finding this...&quot;<br>
<br>
He smiles, and takes the repaired mirror.<br>
<br>
&quot;Being the god of prophecy, being the one alone besides the fates who knows all of past present and future, I believe this would be better off in my hands.&quot; He takes the mirror.<br>
